flowchart TD
    A[System event occurs] --> B{Event type}
    B -->|Application submitted| C[Build applicant confirmation message]
    B -->|Status updated| D[Build status message from template]
    B -->|Interview/SOA/Payout advisory| E[Build schedule/advisory message]
    B -->|Manual office advisory| F[Admin composes custom SMS]

    C --> G[Create notifications row]
    D --> G
    E --> G
    F --> H[Select recipients by filters]
    H --> I[Send single or bulk SMS]
    I --> J[Write sms_logs]

    G --> K{SMS required?}
    K -->|No| L[In-app notification only]
    K -->|Yes| M[sms_send()]
    M --> N{Provider enabled/available?}
    N -->|Yes| O[Send to provider API]
    N -->|No| P[Fallback/dev mode handling]
    O --> Q[Write sms_logs delivery status]
    P --> Q
    Q --> R[Applicant sees update in notifications.php / my-application.php]
    L --> R
